reviewText: Awesome DVD  Grew up in Wsc  Have seen many of the lighthouses
TOO MANY PEOPLE, NOT ENOUGH LIGHTHOUSE

I was looking forward to seeing a rundown of individual lighthouses, which there was some of, but this was mostly interviews with various officials offering their "take" on the general history of lighthouses. There's a lot of old photos. It would be nice if they would have shown some live footage with inside views and a story of the particular families of the lightkeepers. The film came across as boring.
